data.description: WELCOME TO 155 JAY RD , EFFORT PENNSYVANIA ( CHESTNUTHILL TOWNSHIP ) . This home is large and is actually too large for the current owner. Three bedrooms , three full baths, large open floor plan with living room , dinning and kitchen - all open with a beautiful fireplace for the those fall evenings. kitchen is gorgeous and will please any cook. two car garage, two decks, skylights ,   Vaulted ceilings, home is larger than county records and all sizes are approx.  Absolutely a must see and owner said SELL , it is way too large for me. Make your appointment and bring your offers. Ready to make it yours for the Holidays.  Birch Hollow Estates has a lot to offer, indoor pool, tennis ,. basketball courts, playground and club house. low year dues  EST under 400.00 per years. SHOW AND MAKE YOUR OFFERS. THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME WILL BE SOLD!!! This kitchen is absolutely BEAUTIFUL!!!!!
